SHIP-CENTRIC SCENE TEST — "NARRATIVE BEATS" (Milestones):
A beat is an event that significantly shifts the SHIP's physical state, operational capacity,
or fate — whether through construction, modification, combat, decay, or destruction.

[main_key_data]:
  ✓ Events that CHANGE the ship's physical state or destiny (Always count as 1 node).
