  ✗ Environmental descriptions WITHOUT tactical significance.
    e.g., "The sea was blue", "Weather was hot"

  SCENE TEST: "Does this event CHANGE the ship's physical state or fate?"
  If YES → main_key_data. If NO → sub_key_data.
